NAME
    Pod::Translate - Pod translator

SYNOPSIS
     perldoc -L EN -o JA perlpod

INSTALLATION
    To install this module, run the following commands:

     perl Makefile.PL
     make
     make test
     make install

DEPENDENCIES
    <https://github.com/soimort/translate-shell>

